### ========================================
### Management API (via HTTP adapter, port 8080)
### ========================================

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### List all adapters (available + running)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/adapters

### List only available (not yet loaded) adapters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/adapters/available

### Node status (detailed info for orchestrator)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/node/status

### Connect RabbitMQ adapter
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adapters/rabbit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "host": "188.242.193.152",
    "port": 5672,
    "user": "nelos",
    "password": "nelos",
    "vhost": "/",
    "connectionTimeoutSec": 10
}

### Disconnect RabbitMQ adapter
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/adapters/rabbit

### Connect HTTP adapter on a different port
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adapters/http
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "port": 9090,
    "register_url": "",
    "registration_timeout_sec": 10
}

### Disconnect second HTTP adapter
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/adapters/http

### ========================================
### Test API (via HTTP adapter, port 8080)
### ========================================

### Run correctness tests
POST http://localhost:8080/api/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "test_id": "parallel-qsort",
    "test_dir": "C:/Users/Nelos/Desktop/Diploma/C-tests-runner/tests/parallel-qsort",
    "solution_dir": "C:/Users/Nelos/Desktop/Diploma/C-tests-runner/solution",
    "mode": "correctness",
    "threads": 32
}

> {%
    client.global.set("cached_job_id", response.body.job_id);
%}

### Get job result
GET http://localhost:8080/api/jobs/{{cached_job_id}}

### System status (queue overview)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/status

### Cancel a job
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/jobs/{{correctness_job_id}}
